title: A Look Inside Nino Mier Gallery's "Paper (And One on Wood)" Online Viewing Room
description: West Hollywood's Nino Mier Gallery is the next art space to launch an online viewing room to support its entire roster of artists. Aptly titled “PAPER (and one on wood),” the digital presentation largely features works on paper with the exception of one piece…
